Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:29.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:01:59.47,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:34.94,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:01.36,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:39.81,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:16.52,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the bonds that may take root in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed that you might obtain all these Arcana at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It makes my heart flutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4175,5150,\1c&H000000&)}I believe you may be just the person I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Narukami Yu is a student from Class 2-2 at Yasogami High School.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a record of his exciting summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you take your Loveline umbrella with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 7th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It appeared before him without any warning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to grant this wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't even know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Mrs. Nakajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, about your ad for a tutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I have no intention of going to Yasogami High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that no one else could start tutoring right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I was just looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you even any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You betcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 10th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a friend learned he was tutoring,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he asked Narukami Yu to help out at the daycare center.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had no way of knowing that these simple tasks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}would lead to new hardships.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta broke my Neo Featherman robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not broken! Lemme see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't fight—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I expect you to compensate for the toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How much was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I warm your dinner up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nanako. Have you heard of Neo Featherman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone loves him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Heroes these days are something else, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus began Narukami Yu's struggles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a harsh world that revolved around Loveline and Neo Featherman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Neo Featherman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have solved the case, but watch the booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't a chick, what's keeping you out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A fox asked me to pick up a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's put me through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when were you such a tease?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, that was a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, he's right.}I know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 16th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Narukami Yu is once again assaulted by some unforeseen trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do this and—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yuuta said he saw Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I did! I really saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But Loveline only exists in the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Hell in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teddie! What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should act like Teddie and hightail it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What a weird bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not a suspicious bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't his voice sound off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's all stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it doesn't seem natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's normally more, uh, hyperactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how he randomly rolls around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why'd he run from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie's got it bear-y tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 17th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After learning the hardships of labor and the life of Teddie,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Narukami Yu has grown a little more mature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's no time for rest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really cloudy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Earning money is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief! Someone catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She apparently hit her head when the thief pushed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't look serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But my, aren't you cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go hit the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got work.{bitch, please}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'll be out late, so you two can eat without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro said he'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is school fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? It isn't fun for me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always surrounded by idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 18th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer vacation is halfway over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and his interactions with the people around him are beginning to change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're that boy from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you coming to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to visit that elderly woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for an in-patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprisingly forward.{wow, what a whore}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand being a nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The old farts are bossy, and the men leer at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone always leaves me as soon as they recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's good they get discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, let's put that aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know there's going to be a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can breeze through it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you my number, so give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell like alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the daycare center.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I found a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Yuuta isn't really my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from my husband's old marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm still so unsure of how to act around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he hates me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could just relax by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be moving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This town holds too many memories of my late husband for me to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband gave it to me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My love for him had dried up there at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point in hanging onto those old memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I met you here in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the spitting image of my husband in his younger years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tune your TV in to "Tanaka's Amazing Commodities"!\NEnjoy the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's our big commodity for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the legendary fishing pole, the "Explosive Fishing Set"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This indomitable fishing pole will never break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}With this, you'll only need one line and hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Call now, and we'll throw in a set of fishing gear—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a delivery here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Narukami Yu disappears into the light, but his hot summer vacation is still under way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 20th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Narukami Yu's summer vacation is finally reaching its climax.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some major bags under your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wow! I wanna eat some shaved ice!{background Teddie}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Nanako with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Um, all of them!{teddy}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle's bringing her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling we'd run into each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it mean a lot to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed really sad after you threw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy when my husband gave this to me that I couldn't see his face through all my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I truly loved my husband, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in class was promising they'd watch the fireworks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one invited me to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's just jealous of me because they're stupid!{haha what a dumb fuck}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, no one gets fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ruin their nights, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed a picture in your room that said today is your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you choose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a game you can't play by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to ask someone to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone else is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun goofing off with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's what you get for eating so much shaved ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, I stole the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Yuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something wrong with the bitch, then there's something wrong with the pup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is about what I'd expect from a failure of a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's bleeding bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, help her. Please help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My, I didn't think he'd actually call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's bleeding from the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,First, bandage the wound with a long piece of material.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Something long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebi, I need to borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to keep it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, but we're out of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like she'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daddy. I want that big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You're the first person to do anything like this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Told ya she's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure weren't, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Instructor, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might've lost sight of what really matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving lives truly is wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I forgot something so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you helped me remember. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me regain my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall cherish them this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Amagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm with her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to walk in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, you're so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if you get sick again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we took so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a while getting everyone dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' good! Lookin' real good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Thanks for taking care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, didn't you have work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I dumped it on Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pass up on the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave me some cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, why don't we go hit up a shooting booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you guys have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nighttime at a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple leans up against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Unaccustomed to wearing a yukata, it spills open.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the sudden monologue?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural for us to pair off and enjoy the sights!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I agree with Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I've already decided who I'm going with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pair up with Chie, Yuki, and Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how you pair up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, I'll go with all you ladies. {what a playa}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, we suck. We {\i1}really{\i0} suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:23:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the full account of Narukami Yu's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to go on this school trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the boy detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doodly-doo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better leave this kid alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.61,0:24:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the king's orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up!
